{"tid":2101755,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西總統除罩受訪或被控","createTime":"2020-07-10T04:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:40:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2713bbbf534b2ce01d7d000e65144d8adf8e8dd","tid":2101755,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200710/SSYSBQO5NJK7TAMAYS4OU7X7JI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200710%2FSSYSBQO5NJK7TAMAYS4OU7X7JI%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjgZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=ea7d42d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200710%2FSSYSBQO5NJK7TAMAYS4OU7X7JI%2F&h=e4cb4215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200710/SSYSBQO5NJK7TAMAYS4OU7X7JI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n巴西總統除罩受訪或被控<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9L-_0BZw0jh-InvEF_r2cettFLk=/640x409/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OEJAS3MWPLGSCN4ACG7U7MDWPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9L-_0BZw0jh-InvEF_r2cettFLk%3D%2F640x409%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOEJAS3MWPLGSCN4ACG7U7MDWPU.jpg&h=131263e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n染疫的博爾索納羅在記者面前除口罩或遭起訴。<br />\n<br />\n巴西總統博爾索納羅周二公佈確診武漢肺炎，他當日在記者會上未有與在場記者保持社交距離，更一度除下口罩；巴西記者協會表示將入稟最高法院，指控他讓記者蒙受染疫風險。<br />\n<br />\n當日博爾索納羅<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n想展示臉部證明他安好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被斥危及記者生命<br />\n<br />\n巴西記協昨日發聲明指他危及當時在場新聞工作者的生命安全。主席蘇薩說：「國家不能讓這種極不負責任，並構成明確犯罪的行為持續下去而袖手旁觀。」CNN巴西台、巴西紀錄電視台和巴西電視台均有記者出席當日記者會，三間電視台均指暫不會派涉事記者外出採訪，後兩者指記者的病毒檢測呈陰性後才復工。該聯邦地區的記者工會呼籲記者暫停親訪博爾索納羅。<br />\n<br />\n國會議員弗雷索推文稱，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n歸功於服用未證實療效的瘧疾藥羥氯喹。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/路透社"},{"pid":"0db0c2fc40c6038e76e5affba05a8dd2bcfa99eb","tid":2101755,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d08932e5955316408cf0b258e74dfcfce7d0058","tid":2101755,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"just a flu"},{"pid":"867cdd9745de175d9d3945820bb88f536a2db6ea","tid":2101755,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"巴西版侵侵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}